    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 97.</p><p>Heroic Perk: Form of the Elements</p><p>Prerequisite: Conduit</p><p>You gain a fly speed of 60 feet, propelled by your element– jets of flame, arcs of lightning, a howling wind, or a torrent of acid. While flying, you emit your Primordial Element in a 15-foot radius centered on you. Creatures of your choice within this area take 3d8 of your Primordial Element’s damage type at the start of your turn.</p></div>",
